		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Hail to the King, Baby ver 2.0</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.00)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=20430">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=8557">david "khamul" vann</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=8557&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> The Fellowship relies on the Big Three of Aragorn, Boromir, and Arwen. Uruk Shadow side provides the Beatdown.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> January 4, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Hail to the King, Baby--ver 2.0<br>
<br>
Frodo, SoD<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(182)">The One Ring, The Ruling Ring</a><br>
<br>
Fellowship:<br>
<br>
Arwen-starting<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(260)">Legolas, Greenleaf</a>-starting<br>
<br>
Aragorn, KiE x3<br>
Boromir, LoG x2<br>
Ranger&#8217;s Sword x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(256)">Gwemegil</a> x2<br>
