Tale of Gil-Galad<br>
Saga of Elendil<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(15)">Swordsman of the Northern Kingdom</a> x4<br>
A Ranger&#8217;s Versatility x2<br>
Arwen&#8217;s Fate x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(8)">No Stranger to the Shadows</a> x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(1)">The Choice of Luthien</a> <br>
<br>
Shadow:<br>
<br>
Lurtz x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(49)">Uruk Slayer</a> x4<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(29)">Orthanc Assassin</a> x2<br>
